<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4929891>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Harmothoe ruthae sp. nov. (Holotype, IBUFRJ-2132). (A) Dorsal view of the anterior end; (B) first elytron, left side; (C) Middle elytron right side; (D) Right middle parapodium; (E) Detail of microtubercles and posterior margin of elytra; (F) Notochaeta; (G) tip of same chaeta; (H) Bidentate neurochaeta (I) Tip of same chaeta; (J) Tip of unidentate neurochaeta (Scales bars: A= 2 mm; B, C= 200 µm; D= 500 µm; E= 15 µm; F, H= 250 µm; G, I, J= 40 µm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4929891/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4929895>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Harmothoe ruthae sp. nov. chaeta SEM. (A) Notochaeta; (B) tip of lower neurochaeta; (C) tip of upper neurochaeta (Scales bars: A= 100 µm; B, C= 20 µm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4929895/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

